---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Fatima Saleh" description="How Fatima Saleh collects, uses, and protects your personal data.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-10">Last updated: March 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none space-y-8 text-ink/90 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
        <p>
          This website is operated by <strong>Fatima Saleh</strong>, a sole trader based in the United Kingdom.
          For any privacy-related enquiries, you can contact me at:
          <a href="mailto:hello@fatimasaleh.com" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">hello@fatimasaleh.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          As the data controller, I am committed to protecting your personal information and handling it in a
          transparent and responsible manner, in accordance with the UK General Data Protection Regulation
          (UK GDPR) and the Data Protection Act 2018.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. What data we collect</h2>
        <p>When you use the contact form on this website, I collect the following personal data:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Name</strong> — so I know who I'm speaking with</li>
          <li><strong>Email address</strong> — so I can reply to your enquiry</li>
          <li><strong>Message content</strong> — the details of your enquiry or request</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          This data is submitted via <a href="https://web3forms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">Web3Forms</a>,
          a third-party form processing service. Web3Forms forwards completed submissions to my email address and
          retains data in accordance with their own privacy policy.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          I do not currently use any analytics tools, advertising pixels, or third-party tracking services on this site.
          No cookies are set for tracking purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. How we use your data</h2>
        <p>Your personal data is used solely to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Respond to your enquiry or message</li>
          <li>Follow up on a coaching, consulting, or collaboration request you have initiated</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          The lawful basis for processing is <strong>legitimate interests</strong> (responding to a message you have
          voluntarily sent) and, where relevant, <strong>contract performance</strong> (if your enquiry leads to
          a working arrangement).
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          I will never sell, share, or disclose your personal data to any third party for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Data retention</h2>
        <p>
          I retain correspondence (including contact form submissions forwarded to my email) for up to
          <strong>12 months</strong> from the date of last contact. After this period, messages are deleted unless
          an ongoing business relationship requires longer retention.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Your rights</h2>
        <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of the personal data I hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — ask me to correct inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
          <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — request that I delete your personal data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li><strong>Restriction</strong> — ask me to limit how I use your data in certain circumstances</li>
          <li><strong>Objection</strong> — object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
          <li><strong>Portability</strong> — receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          To exercise any of these rights, please email
          <a href="mailto:hello@fatimasaleh.com" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">hello@fatimasaleh.com</a>.
          I will respond within 30 days.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          If you are not satisfied with how I handle your data, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the
          <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">Information Commissioner's Office (ICO)</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This site stores a single preference key (<code class="bg-cream/60 px-1 rounded text-sm">cookie_consent</code>) in
          your browser's <code class="bg-cream/60 px-1 rounded text-sm">localStorage</code> to remember whether you have
          accepted or dismissed the cookie notice. This is a functional preference, not a tracking cookie, and
          is not shared with any third party.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          For full details, see the <a href="/cookie-policy" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">Cookie Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          I may update this privacy policy from time to time. The date at the top of this page indicates
          when it was last revised. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the
          updated policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any questions about this policy or how your data is handled, please contact:<br />
          <strong>Fatima Saleh</strong><br />
          <a href="mailto:hello@fatimasaleh.com" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">hello@fatimasaleh.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
